Package: tinyviztest
Type: Package
Title: Snapshots for unit tests using the `tinytest` framework
Version: 0.0.0.9007
Author: Vincent Arel-Bundock
Maintainer: Vincent Arel-Bundock <vincent.arel-bundock@umontreal.ca>
Description: Use the `tinytest` framekwork to compare plots and console printouts to known snapshots ("golden tests"). Supports base `R` and `ggplot2` plots.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Imports:
    diffobj,
    magick,
    tinytest
Suggests:
    ggplot2,
    ragg,
    svglite
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
